DESCRIPTION:Join CAPS staff for a low commitment\, all welcome\, introduct
 ory Mindfulness in nature experience. The focus of Mindfulness in the Mea
 dow is creating a sense of community\, calm\, and practicing self-care. Y
 ou will have the chance to learn Mindful coping skills to help you feel c
 onnected\, regulated\, and at peace! Join one or many sessions\, as we wi
 ll have this opportunity throughout the summer.A staff member will have a
  sign with them at the location. If you have any questions\, you can cont
 act CAPS by calling 812-855-5711.\n\nHosted by: Counseling and Psychologi
 cal Services (CAPS)\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://be
 involved.indiana.edu/event/12310317
